Package: monitor-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 18.0.0)
Maintainer: Monitoring Platform <ops@example.com>
Description: Cybersecurity & server metrics monitoring agent
 Lightweight Node.js agent that collects CPU, memory, disk and network
 metrics plus SSH/sudo/firewall security events and securely streams them
 to the central monitoring platform. Runs as a systemd service with
 offline buffering and automatic retry.
